#. HTML: </h3><p>
#. REF: sc14, pts-vp-pli4.73, pts-cs-bu-pc32.5, ms2V_691
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc32:5.1"
msgid "Tena kho pana samayena bhikkhū manussehi saddhiṃ addhānaṃ gacchanti."
msgstr "Soon afterwards monks went traveling on a main road with some people."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc32:5.2"
msgid "Atha kho te bhikkhū te manusse etadavocuṃ—"
msgstr "The monks said to the people,"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc32:5.3"
msgid "“muhuttaṃ, āvuso, āgametha; piṇḍāya carissāmā”ti."
msgstr "“Please wait a moment while we walk for alms.”"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc32:5.4"
msgid "Te evamāhaṃsu—"
msgstr "They replied,"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc32:5.5"
msgid "“idheva, bhante, bhuñjathā”ti."
msgstr "“Venerables, please eat right here.”"

#. REF: pts-vp-en.2.309
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc32:5.6"
msgid "Bhikkhū kukkuccāyantā na paṭiggaṇhanti—“paṭikkhittaṃ bhagavatā gaṇabhojanan”ti."
msgstr "Knowing that the Master had prohibited eating meals in a group and being afraid of wrongdoing, they did not accept."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc32:5.7"
msgid "Bhagavato etamatthaṃ ārocesuṃ … pe …"
msgstr "They told the Master. …"

#. HTML: <span class="rule"> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc32:5.8"
msgid "anujānāmi, bhikkhave, addhānagamanasamaye gaṇabhojanaṃ bhuñjituṃ."
msgstr "“Monks, I allow you to eat in a group when you are traveling on a main road."

#. HTML: </span> 
